### **Phase 1B: Trading Fee Discounts**
*Reward BC400 holders with reduced trading costs*

**Implementation:**
```solidity
function calculateFeeDiscount(address user) returns (uint256) {
    uint256 balance = BC400.balanceOf(user);
    
    if (balance >= 100_000_000 * 1e9) return 50; // 50% discount
    if (balance >= 50_000_000 * 1e9) return 30;  // 30% discount
    if (balance >= 10_000_000 * 1e9) return 15;  // 15% discount
    return 0; // No discount
}

// Apply in buyShares:
uint256 baseFee = (cost * protocolFee) / 10000;
uint256 discount = calculateFeeDiscount(msg.sender);
uint256 finalFee = baseFee - (baseFee * discount / 100);
```

**Impact:**
- High-volume traders incentivized to hold BC400
- Creates natural buy pressure
- Reduces sell pressure (holding > selling)

